---
import ConstructLayout from '../layouts/ConstructLayout.astro';
---

<ConstructLayout title="Revista - Cosmopolitican">
  <div class="revista-header">
    <div class="block-header" style="transform: rotate(2deg);">ARCHIVOS & EDICIONES</div>
    
    <div class="archive-grid">
      <article class="issue-card featured">
        <div class="issue-number">Nº 01</div>
        <h2>EL DESPERTAR</h2>
        <p>Manifiesto sobre la modernidad tardía y el rol del arte en el sur. Una exploración de los cimientos estéticos.</p>
        <button class="cta-button">LEER AHORA</button>
      </article>
      
      <article class="issue-card">
        <div class="issue-number">Nº 00</div>
        <h2>PRÓLOGO</h2>
        <p>Borradores, ideas sueltas y el manifiesto original perdido.</p>
        <button class="cta-button">EXAMINAR</button>
      </article>
      
       <article class="issue-card dark">
        <div class="issue-number">EXTRA</div>
        <h2>POESÍA VISUAL</h2>
        <p>Selección de fotomontajes constructivistas y gráfica radical.</p>
        <button class="cta-button" style="border-color: var(--c-bg); box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--c-bg);">VER COLECCIÓN</button>
      </article>
      
      <article class="issue-card">
        <div class="issue-number">Nº -1</div>
        <h2>RUINAS</h2>
        <p>Lo que construimos sobre los escombros del pasado.</p>
        <button class="cta-button">DESCUBRIR</button>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</ConstructLayout>

<style>
  .revista-header {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .archive-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .issue-card {
    background-color: var(--c-bg);
    border: 6px solid var(--c-black);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--c-black);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .issue-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    right: -20px;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background-color: var(--c-red);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    border-bottom: 6px solid var(--c-black);
  }

  .issue-card:hover {
    transform: translate(-4px, -4px);
    box-shadow: 16px 16px 0 var(--c-red);
  }

  .issue-card.featured {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    background-color: var(--c-red);
    box-shadow: 15px 15px 0 var(--c-black);
    border: 8px solid var(--c-black);
  }

  .issue-card.featured::before {
    background-color: var(--c-bg);
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
  }

  .issue-card.dark {
    background-color: var(--c-black);
    color: var(--c-bg);
    border-color: var(--c-red);
    box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--c-red);
  }

  .issue-card.dark::before {
    background-color: var(--c-bg);
  }

  .issue-number {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--c-black);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  }

  .issue-card.featured .issue-number {
    font-size: 6rem;
  }

  .issue-card.dark .issue-number {
    -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--c-bg);
  }

  .issue-card h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 6px solid currentColor;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .issue-card.featured h2 {
    font-size: 4rem;
  }

  .issue-card p {
    flex: 1;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .issue-card .cta-button {
    align-self: flex-start;
    margin-top: auto;
  }
</style>
